What s new in 3.0: Meet our brand new design. Every pixel is taken care of to make your crystalizing journey flawless. New tasty features: Bloom Shine Color Presets Use Bloom to add a blurry foggy effect to your crystalized art. Make it fogy and mysterious just like you are. Use Shine to guess what... Make it shine. So shine bright like a diamond. Use Color Presets to spice up your art with beautiful filters. You deserve only the best filters so we made them for you. Added a variety of formatting options your gorgeous portraits demands unconventional framing. Now you can crystalize videos with unlimited length. 10 hour video of your sunny selfie crystalized Easy. Fixed a lot of minor issues and nasty bugs. Nothing to worry about. Don t forget to use hashtag crystaliq to get in our Instagram collection of beautiful people from around the world. Your photos videos look brilliant with Crystaliq.

Crystallized videos are up to 60 times per second better than static photos. In this major update we ve developed a special crystal algorithm in the app so that you will not have to break your iPhone lens to make such videos. In this release: Select up to 30 seconds of any video from your iPhone and make it brilliant. Choose from 14 unique filters to apply to your video with limitless editing options. Record grid animation while you rotate and scale it on top of your video. Add aberration edges blur displacement and 3D moving to the video. Export to Instagram Snapchat VSCO or wherever you want with original sound and brilliant effect. Crystaliq your photos and videos look brilliant!
